Package: TailorBayes
Type: Package
Title: Markov Chain Monte Carlo for Tailored Bayesian inference
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Solon", "Karapanagiotis", email = "Solon.karapanagiotis@mrc-bsu.cam.ac.uk",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: 
    Contains functions to perform Tailored Bayesian inference for binary classification.   Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) is used to simulate the posterior. The output is a 'coda' mcmc object that can then be summarised using the 'coda' package. 
URL: https://github.com/solonkarapa/TailorBayes
